Title and reference

   Regulation (EU) No 1169/2011 of the European Parliament and of the
   Council of 25 October 2011 on the provision of food information to
   consumers, amending Regulations (EC) No 1924/2006 and (EC) No 1925/2006
   of the European Parliament and of the Council, and repealing Commission
   Directive 87/250/EEC, Council Directive 90/496/EEC, Commission
   Directive 1999/10/EC, Directive 2000/13/EC of the European Parliament
   and of the Council, Commission Directives 2002/67/EC and 2008/5/EC and
   Commission Regulation (EC) No 608/2004 Text with EEA relevance

   Regulation (EU) No 1169/2011 of the European Parliament and of the
   Council of 25 October 2011 on the provision of food information to
   consumers, amending Regulations (EC) No 1924/2006 and (EC) No 1925/2006
   of the European Parliament and of the Council, and repealing Commission
   Directive 87/250/EEC, Council Directive 90/496/EEC, Commission
   Directive 1999/10/EC, Directive 2000/13/EC of the European Parliament
   and of the Council, Commission Directives 2002/67/EC and 2008/5/EC and
   Commission Regulation (EC) No 608/2004 Text with EEA relevance

   Regulation (EU) No 1169/2011 of the European Parliament and of the
   Council of 25 October 2011 on the provision of food information to
   consumers, amending Regulations (EC) No 1924/2006 and (EC) No 1925/2006
   of the European Parliament and of the Council, and repealing Commission
   Directive 87/250/EEC, Council Directive 90/496/EEC, Commission
   Directive 1999/10/EC, Directive 2000/13/EC of the European Parliament
   and of the Council, Commission Directives 2002/67/EC and 2008/5/EC and
   Commission Regulation (EC) No 608/2004 Text with EEA relevance

